Sersan Kepala, kau mengecewakanku.

209
00:09:26,136 --> 00:09:27,972
Komandan Rossi, karena kau di sini...

210
00:09:28,055 --> 00:09:29,807
Mungkin kau bisa memberi tahu
Sersan Kepala...

211
00:09:29,891 --> 00:09:32,602
