212
00:09:32,686 --> 00:09:34,313
Dan tak lebih dari itu.

213
00:09:37,024 --> 00:09:38,526
Entahlah, aku angkatan darat.

214
00:09:41,822 --> 00:09:43,073
Kau juga tak tahu?

215
00:09:43,157 --> 00:09:45,743
XO, coba jelaskan pada mereka.

216
00:09:45,826 --> 00:09:47,871
Jembatan Brooklyn berada
di ketinggian 39 meter...

217
00:09:47,954 --> 00:09:49,039
Di Sungai East.

218
00:09:49,122 --> 00:09:51,500
Dan Montana dibangun
di Pangkalan Angkatan Laut Brooklyn.

219
00:09:51,584 --> 00:09:53,127
Oleh wanita.

220
00:09:53,962 --> 00:09:56,297
